text: The Alor Gajah Square () or Keris Square () is a town square in Alor Gajah Town, Alor Gajah, Melaka, Malaysia. ==Architecture== The square features the Kris Landmark, a large bronze sculpture of a kris. ==See also== * List of tourist attractions in Melaka ==References== Category:Squares in Malacca
title: Alor Gajah Square
